{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dynamic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"motionSensitivity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"motionSensitivity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"motionSensitivity","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)motionSensitivity","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"title":"motionSensitivity"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/motionSensitivity","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The sensitivity to device motion. The lower the value the less motion of the device is required to prevent the scanner from entering energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to 4.0"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/motionsensitivity"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/motionsensitivity"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.3"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/motionSensitivity":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"motionSensitivity","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The sensitivity to device motion. The lower the value the less motion of the device is required to prevent the scanner from entering energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 4.0","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"motionSensitivity","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"motionSensitivity","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/motionSensitivity","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/motionsensitivity"}},"vari